      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for your next great project? This vehicle is ready for some serious TLC and is the perfect candidate for a full restoration or a dedicated parts donor! While it has seen better days and currently shows significant wear throughout, it offers a fantastic foundation for any mechanical enthusiast looking to roll up their sleeves. Grab this diamond in the rough and bring it back to life!",
